12:39.467 --> 12:42.010
You mean, changed
as a result of his work?

12:42.095 --> 12:43.554
Yes, his work.

12:44.013 --> 12:46.557
His insane ambition
to create life.

12:47.851 --> 12:49.852
How? How?

12:51.896 --> 12:54.398
Please tell us everything,
whatever it is.

12:54.858 --> 12:58.152
The bodies we use
in our dissecting room
for lecture purposes

12:58.236 --> 13:01.196
