what l mean.

13:25.555 --> 13:28.891
Herr Frankenstein
was interested
only in human life.

13:29.559 --> 13:32.728
First to destroy it,
then recreate it.

13:33.563 --> 13:36.315
There you have
his mad dream.

13:39.736 --> 13:41.528
Can we go to him?

13:41.613 --> 13:42.821
You will not be
very welcome.

13:42.906 --> 13:45.741
Oh, what does that matter?
l must see him.

13:46.326 --> 13:49.328
Dr. Waldman, you have
influence with Henry.

13:49.913 --> 13:51.455
Won't you come with us?

13:51.581 --> 13:54.583
l'm sorry,
but Herr Frankenstein
is no longer my pupil.

13:55.752 --> 13:57.461
But he respects you.

13:58.421 --> 14:00.380
Won't you help us
to take him away?

14:00.465 --> 14:03.091
Very well, FrÃ¤ulein.
l've warned you.

14:03.468 --> 14:05.761
But if you wish it,
l will go.

14:11.768 --> 14:13.185
(WlND HOWLlNG)

14:13.686 --> 14:15.395
(THUNDER RUMBLlNG)

14:29.452 --> 14:30.577
Fritz!

14:31.162 --> 14:32.162
Hello.

14:32.288 --> 14:33.372
(RATTLlNG)

