those connections?

14:36.042 --> 14:37.376
Yes, they're done.

14:37.460 --> 14:40.212
Well, come down then
and help with
these attachments.

14:40.296 --> 14:41.964
We've lots to do.

14:42.966 --> 14:44.299
(THUNDER RUMBLlNG)

14:58.273 --> 14:59.398
