15:54.370 --> 15:56.538
No blood, no decay.

15:57.415 --> 15:59.207
Just a few stitches.

16:01.210 --> 16:04.254
And look,
here's the final touch.

16:08.551 --> 16:11.094
The brain
you stole, Fritz.
Yes.

16:11.220 --> 16:14.056
Think of it.
The brain of
a dead man,

16:14.307 --> 16:18.226
waiting to live again
in a body l made
with my own hands.

16:19.228 --> 16:20.896
With my own hands.

16:24.233 --> 16:26.902
Let's have one final test.
Throw the switches.

16:32.575 --> 16:33.700
(WHlRRlNG)

16:35.161 --> 16:36.453
(DRONlNG)

16:39.123 --> 16:41.041
