you want to come in?

19:55.945 --> 19:57.279
Very well.

20:16.048 --> 20:19.843
Forgive me,
but l'm forced to take
unusual precautions.

20:24.223 --> 20:25.849
Sit down, please.

20:28.144 --> 20:29.519
Sit down !

20:34.734 --> 20:36.484
You too, Elizabeth.

20:37.069 --> 20:38.194
Please.

20:41.198 --> 20:44.367
A moment ago,
you said l was crazy.

20:45.328 --> 20:47.037
Tomorrow
we'll see about that.

20:47.121 --> 20:48.371
Don't touch that!

20:53.544 --> 20:56.838
l'm sorry, Doctor,
but l insist.

21:09.685 --> 21:10.852
Please.

21:16.734 --> 21:20.987
Dr. Waldman,
l learned a great deal
from you at the university

21:21.072 --> 21:24.199
about the violet ray,
the ultraviolet ray,

21:24.533 --> 21:27.911
which you said was
the highest color
in the spectrum.

21:28.704 --> 21:30.205
You were wrong.

21:31.374 --> 21:34.960
Here in this machinery,
l have gone beyond that.

21:37.546 --> 21:42.092
l have discovered
the great ray that first
brought life into the world.

21:42.218 --> 21:44.135
Oh. And your proof?

21:44.971 --> 21:47.430
Tonight you shall
have your proof.

21:49.392 --> 21:52.435
At first, l experimented
only with dead animals

21:52.895 --> 21:56.898
and then a human heart,
which l kept beating
for three weeks.

21:58.067 --> 21:59.275
But now,

22:00.069 --> 22:03.238
l'm going to turn
that ray on that body

22:03.489 --> 22:05.407
and endow it with life.

22:05.908 --> 22:09.452
And you really believe
that you can bring
life to the dead?

22:10.329 --> 22:12.497
That body is not dead.

22:12.915 --> 22:14.582
lt has never lived.

22:15.751 --> 22:17.252
l created it.

22:17.628 --> 22:21.548
l made it with my own hands
from the bodies
l took from graves,

22:21.632 --> 22:23.758
from the gallows, anywhere!

22:27.096 --> 22:28.805
Go and see for yourself.

22:31.642 --> 22:32.934
You, too.

22:38.274 --> 22:40.025
Dead, eh?

22:47.950 --> 22:50.160
Quite a good scene, isn't it?

22:50.619 --> 22:55.498
One man crazy,
three very sane spectators.

22:55.958 --> 22:57.167
(RATTLlNG)

22:57.251 --> 22:58.460
(THUNDERCLAP)

22:58.794 --> 23:00.879
ls everything ready?
Yes!

23:01.005 --> 23:02.881
