23:07.011 --> 23:08.178
(ELECTRlClTY CRACKLlNG)

23:08.846 --> 23:10.722
(TALKlNG lNDlSTlNCTLY)

23:14.143 --> 23:15.143
(BUZZlNG)

23:21.859 --> 23:23.276
(THUNDER RUMBLlNG)

23:40.086 --> 23:41.836
(BUZZlNG CONTlNUES)

23:57.520 --> 23:59.646
(LOUD ELECTRlC BUZZlNG)

24:00.272 --> 24:01.356
(lNAUDlBLE)

24:06.862 --> 24:08.113
(ELECTRlClTY CRACKLlNG)

24:11.867 --> 24:13.076
(THUNDER CLAPPlNG)

24:22.711 --> 24:24.546
(THUNDER lNTENSlFlES)

24:33.389 --> 24:34.889
